@startuml
[*] -> PromptPIN : Insert card
PromptPIN --> VerifyPIN : Enter PIN
VerifyPIN : PIN verified successfully -> OptionsAvailable : Provide options to user
OptionsAvailable --> ProcessWithdrawal : User selects withdrawal
ProcessWithdrawal --> DispenseCash : Process withdrawal request
DispenseCash --> PrintReceipt : Print receipt for transaction
PrintReceipt --> ReturnCard : Return card to user
ReturnCard --> ResetSystem : System resets after brief moment
ResetSystem -> [*] : Ready for next user
@enduml
